# Levels:
# 0: under 120 m, zoom 24, city
# 1: under 300 m, zoom 23, hiking
# 2: under 2 km, zoom 20, cycling
# 3: under 8 km, zoom 18, car
# 4: under 30 km, zoom 16, overview
# 5: zoom 0, overview


